Abu Dhabi
3 X Field Service Engineer - French Speaking Abu Dhabi Salary AED 30,000 - AED 35,000 per month DOE + AED 250 per day when working away + Pension + 25 days holiday + rest and Recuperation
THE COMPANY Our client is a market leader in the supply of rotating equipment solutions that are custom engineered for applications in the energy industry. The company has a stable and growing presence in the worldwide market with the security expected from an organisation of this stature. Priding itself on its levels of quality and workmanship, the company now has opportunities for a number of French speaking Field Service Engineers to join a successful installation and maintenance team based in Abu Dhabi.
THE ROLE As a Field Service Engineer your role will include:
Hands-on repair of rotating equipment including gas and steam turbines, compressors, reciprocal, turbo and centrifugal machinery First hand contact with clients and other engineers Fault finding on machinery and solution planning quickly and efficiently Following all company Health and Safety procedures
THE CANDIDATE The ideal Field Service Engineer will have the following:
Ability to speak French fluently is essential Experience working with rotating machinery Specialist knowledge of inspecting, disassembling and reassembling gas and steam turbines, reciprocating, centrifugal, gas and steam compressors to OEM standards Strong people skills and act as an ambassador for the company Excellent problem solving and communication abilities The ability to lead a team and/or work unsupervised on tasks to a high standard Qualified to HND / HNC level in a relevant discipline.
THE BENEFITS The successful Field Service Engineer can expect
Excellent Earning potential Opportunity to work within a successful team Pension Expenses Security
If you are looking for your next exciting career opportunity please contact: Jonathan Clarke on or email
